Package: STAT600.HW1.SLM
Title: Univariate OLS Linear Regression
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Wentao", "Guo",
    email = "Wentao.Guo@colostate.edu",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Performs a simple OLS Gaussian linear regression for one numerical 
    predictor on one numerical response. Outputs the coefficients estimates, 
    their corresponding standard errors and 95% confidence intervals, as well as 
    the fitted values and model residuals.
